---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout>

<!-- Full-page frosted glass entry overlay -->
<div id="page-overlay" class="page-overlay" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="overlay-name">
  <div class="overlay-card">
    <img class="overlay-avatar" src="/assets/headshot.png" alt="Michael Frost" />
    <div class="overlay-name" id="overlay-name">Michael Frost</div>
    <div class="overlay-role">Director of AI &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; VP of Technology</div>
    <div class="overlay-links">
      <a class="overlay-link" id="overlay-schedule" href="#" onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url:'https://calendly.com/mike-ageniusailabs/30min'});return false;">Let's talk</a>
      <span class="overlay-link-sep">&middot;</span>
      <a class="overlay-link" id="overlay-see-work" href="#work">See the Work</a>
    </div>
    <button class="overlay-cta" id="overlay-cta" type="button">Get to Know Me</button>
    <div class="overlay-powered">Powered by Python &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Claude &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; ElevenLabs</div>
  </div>
</div>

  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
      <span class="nav-dot"></span>
      MF
    </a>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <a href="https://ageniusailabs.com" class="nav-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Agenius AI Labs</a>
<a href="#" class="nav-cta" onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url:'https://calendly.com/mike-ageniusailabs/30min'});return false;">Let's talk</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero" id="hero">
    <div class="hero-left" id="hero-left">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <div class="hero-dateline">
          <span class="hero-serial">№ 01</span>
          <span class="hero-sep">·</span>
          <span>Portfolio — MMXXVI</span>
        </div>
        <h1><span class="hero-given">Michael</span><span class="hero-family">Frost</span></h1>
        <div class="open-pill"><span class="pill-dot"></span>Open to Director / VP AI Roles</div>
        <p class="hero-pitch"><em>Twenty years</em> of building IT systems. <em>Three years</em> building the automations that run business.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a href="#" class="btn-primary" onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url:'https://calendly.com/mike-ageniusailabs/30min'});return false;">Let's talk</a>
          <a href="#work" class="btn-ghost">See the work</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-chat" id="hero-chat">
        <div class="chat-label" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="chat-dot"></span>
          <span>Live · Interactive Portfolio</span>
          <span class="chat-sep">·</span>
          <span>RAG over my career</span>
        </div>
        <iframe id="chat-iframe" src="https://ask-michael.ageniusailabs.com?embed=1" title="Ask Michael AI" allow="microphone"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-photo">
      <img src="/assets/headshot.png" alt="Michael Frost" loading="eager" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="strip">
    <div class="strip-inner">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-numblock">
          <span class="stat-num">20</span>
          <span class="stat-unit">years</span>
        </div>
        <span class="stat-label">leading IT and technology across government, enterprise, and services</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-numblock">
          <span class="stat-num">3</span>
          <span class="stat-unit">sectors</span>
        </div>
        <span class="stat-label">government, enterprise, and services — every environment that makes a technology leader</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-numblock">
          <span class="stat-num">100<span class="stat-plus">+</span></span>
          <span class="stat-unit">automations</span>
        </div>
        <span class="stat-label">running in production across the businesses I operate</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-left">
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-sq"></span>§ 02 · Who I am</div>
        <div class="accent-bar"></div>
        <h2 class="about-h2">Twenty years building the technology companies actually run on.</h2>
        <ol class="career-timeline" aria-label="Career arc">
          <li><span class="tl-year">2005</span><span class="tl-role">contractor</span></li>
          <li><span class="tl-year">2012</span><span class="tl-role">lead</span></li>
          <li><span class="tl-year">2018</span><span class="tl-role">director</span></li>
          <li><span class="tl-year">2023</span><span class="tl-role">founder</span></li>
          <li><span class="tl-year">2026</span><span class="tl-role">operator</span></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="mono-location">New York City · London</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-body">
        <p>My first decade was enterprise network engineering. I worked as a government contractor on some of the largest enterprise networks in the country, operating under national security standards where uptime, security, and process discipline are not optional. That environment shaped how I think about every system I have built since.</p>
        <p>From there I moved into IT leadership across enterprise and managed services, growing and running teams through acquisitions and organizational change. I learned what it takes to keep infrastructure stable not just technically, but organizationally through the gap between executive decisions and operational reality.</p>
        <p class="thesis">I am not an AI person who discovered business. I am a technology leader who spent twenty years learning how systems fail, how teams scale, and how executives make decisions. I apply that to AI now, because AI is where the next wave of operating leverage lives, and because most companies do not yet have someone in the room who can translate between the boardroom and the build. That is the role I am looking for next.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Signature moment: oversized vermillion MF ligature as section transition. Executed once, nothing else rotated. -->
  <div class="signature-band" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="signature-mf">MF</span>
  </div>

  <section class="work" id="work">
    <div class="work-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-sq"></span>§ 03 · Selected work</div>
        <h2 class="section-h2">AI systems built and running in production.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="work-grid">

        <article class="work-card work-card-hero">
          <span class="card-tag">Featured — IT Services · AI</span>
          <h3 class="card-title">Managed Services AI Platform</h3>
          <div class="card-metric card-metric-hero">
            <span class="metric-num">6</span>
            <span class="metric-label">organizations unified on one platform</span>
          </div>
          <p class="card-desc">Designed and built the AI and automation layer for a managed services operation, unifying systems, client workflows, and operational visibility across the business.</p>
          <a href="https://ageniusailabs.com/work/bwit-ai-platform" class="card-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View case study <span class="arr">→</span></a>
        </article>

        <article class="work-card">
          <span class="card-tag">E-commerce · Automation</span>
          <h3 class="card-title">AI Product Photography Studio</h3>
          <div class="card-metric"><span class="metric-num">$0.06</span><span class="metric-label">per photo at scale</span></div>
          <p class="card-desc">An end-to-end AI pipeline that replaced traditional product photography for a consumer brand, from prompt to approved asset.</p>
          <a href="https://ageniusailabs.com/work/cantique-photo-studio" class="card-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View case study <span class="arr">→</span></a>
        </article>

        <article class="work-card">
          <span class="card-tag">Social Media · AI Pipeline</span>
          <h3 class="card-title">Autonomous Content Pipeline</h3>
          <div class="card-metric"><span class="metric-num">0<span class="metric-unit">hrs</span></span><span class="metric-label">manual effort per week, once running</span></div>
          <p class="card-desc">Fully autonomous content production and publishing — ideation, image generation, scheduling, performance tracking.</p>
          <a href="https://ageniusailabs.com/work/agenius-3d-pipeline/" class="card-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View case study <span class="arr">→</span></a>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="contact-inner">
      <div class="contact-left">
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-sq"></span>§ 04 · Get in touch</div>
        <h2 class="contact-h2">Open to the right Director or VP AI role.</h2>
        <p class="contact-sub">If you are building an AI team or transforming a technology organization and need someone who has done it end to end, I would like to hear about it.</p>
        <div class="contact-links">
          <a href="#" class="contact-link-btn" onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url:'https://calendly.com/mike-ageniusailabs/30min'});return false;">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg>
            Let's talk
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/michael-frostbutter/" class="contact-link-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-right">
        <div class="contact-detail-card">
          <div class="detail-row"><span class="detail-label">Based</span><span class="detail-val">New York City · London</span></div>
          <div class="detail-row"><span class="detail-label">Roles</span><span class="detail-val">Director of AI, VP of AI, VP of Technology</span></div>
          <div class="detail-row"><span class="detail-label">Availability</span><span class="detail-val">Interviewing now</span></div>
          <div class="detail-row"><span class="detail-label">Work auth</span><span class="detail-val">US Citizen · UK eligible</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-rule"></div>
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <span class="colophon-mark">MF</span>
      <div class="colophon-meta">
        <span class="colophon-label">Colophon</span>
        <span class="colophon-text">Set in <em>Fraunces</em>, <em>Hanken Grotesk</em>, and <em>Martian Mono</em>. Ink on paper. April, MMXXVI.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="colophon-links">
        <a href="#" onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url:'https://calendly.com/mike-ageniusailabs/30min'});return false;">Schedule</a>
        <a href="https://ageniusailabs.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Agenius AI Labs ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  nav {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: var(--z-nav);
    height: 60px;
    background: rgba(244, 241, 234, 0.88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px) saturate(1.2);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px) saturate(1.2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 500; font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--ink); text-decoration: none;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.625rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .nav-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); }
  .nav-right {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .nav-link { color: var(--ink-mute); text-decoration: none; transition: color 180ms; font-weight: 500; }
  .nav-link:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  .nav-cta {
    color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none; transition: color 180ms;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  .hero {
    height: 100vh; min-height: 640px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-left {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden; height: 100%;
    max-height: 100vh;
  }
  .hero-text {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    padding: 5rem clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 4rem) 5rem clamp(2rem, 7vw, 7rem);
    transition: padding 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }
  /* Chat panel — hidden below until reveal */
  .hero-chat {
    flex: 1; min-height: 0;
    max-height: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(56px);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.85s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
                opacity 0.5s ease 0.15s,
                transform 0.6s ease 0.1s;
    padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 4rem) 0 clamp(2rem, 7vw, 7rem);
  }
  .chat-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.625rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    padding-bottom: 0.625rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }
  .chat-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(194, 77, 44, 0.18);
    animation: chat-breathe 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .chat-sep { opacity: 0.4; }
  @keyframes chat-breathe {
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(194, 77, 44, 0.18); }
    50%      { box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(194, 77, 44, 0.08); }
  }
  .hero-chat iframe {
    display: block; width: 100%; height: calc(100% - 2rem);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 0 0 var(--ink);
    background: #0a0a0f;
  }
  /* Revealed state — hero-text compresses up, chat fills remaining height */
  .hero-left.chat-revealed .hero-text {
    padding-top: 2.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.25rem;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }
  .hero-left.chat-revealed .hero-chat {
    max-height: 100dvh;
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    overflow: visible;
  }
  .hero-photo {
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-photo img {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover; object-position: top center;
    display: block;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .hero {
      height: auto; min-height: 0;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      overflow: visible;
    }
    .hero-photo {
      order: -1;
      width: 180px; height: 180px;
      margin: 2rem auto 0;
      border-radius: 50%;
      overflow: hidden;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.18), 0 0 0 4px rgba(56,189,248,0.15);
    }
    .hero-photo img { object-position: center 20%; }
    .hero-left {
      flex: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      max-height: none; overflow: visible; height: auto;
    }
    .hero-text { padding: 2.5rem clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem) 1.5rem; }
    .hero-chat {
      flex: none;
      max-height: none;
      overflow: visible;
      padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem) 2rem;
    }
    .hero-left.chat-revealed .hero-chat {
      max-height: none;
      overflow: visible;
    }
    .hero-chat iframe { height: 640px; }
    .cta-row { flex-wrap: nowrap; }
    .cta-row .btn-primary,
    .cta-row .btn-ghost {
      flex: 1 1 0;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      text-align: center;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-chat iframe { height: 620px; }
    .cta-row .btn-primary,
    .cta-row .btn-ghost {
      padding: 0.75rem 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
  }
  /* Editorial status stamp — hairline rules, wider tracking, no fill */
  .open-pill {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.625rem;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 0.625rem 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
    width: fit-content;
  }
  .pill-dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #16a34a;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.18);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-mute);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.625rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .eyebrow-sq { width: 14px; height: 1px; background: var(--ink-mute); flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* Hero dateline — small mono line above name, magazine masthead feel */
  .hero-dateline {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-mute);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.875rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    max-width: 32ch;
  }
  .hero-serial { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }
  .hero-sep { opacity: 0.4; }

  /* Hero name — Fraunces display, confident scale, tight leading */
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 9.5vw, 8.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144, "SOFT" 0, "WONK" 1;
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .hero-given { display: block; }
  .hero-family {
    display: block;
    font-style: italic;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144, "SOFT" 30, "WONK" 1;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-left: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 2.5rem);
  }

  .hero-pitch {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 1.4vw, 1.375rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 24;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 42ch;
    margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
  }
  .hero-pitch em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 24, "SOFT" 50;
  }
  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  /* Editorial CTAs — hairline underline, mono caps, no fills */
  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  .btn-primary, .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--ink);
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 0.5rem 0 0.4rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    transition: color 200ms ease, border-color 200ms ease, gap 200ms ease;
  }
  .btn-primary { color: var(--accent); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }
  .btn-primary::after { content: '↗'; font-size: 1em; transition: transform 220ms ease; }
  .btn-ghost::after { content: '→'; font-size: 1em; transition: transform 220ms ease; }
  .btn-primary:hover { gap: 0.75rem; color: var(--accent-hi); border-bottom-color: var(--accent-hi); }
  .btn-primary:hover::after { transform: translate(2px, -2px); }
  .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--accent); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); gap: 0.75rem; }
  .btn-ghost:hover::after { transform: translateX(3px); }

  /* Editorial stats — magazine pull-out feel, on paper not dark band */
  .strip { background: var(--paper); padding: 7rem 0 8rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .strip-inner {
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3.25rem;
  }
  .stat {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr; gap: 3rem;
    align-items: baseline;
    padding-top: 1.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    position: relative;
  }
  .stat-numblock { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144, "SOFT" 0, "WONK" 1;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 7vw, 6.5rem);
    font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .stat-plus { font-size: 0.55em; vertical-align: 0.35em; color: var(--accent); margin-left: 0.1em; }
  .stat-unit {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-mute);
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.0625rem, 1.25vw, 1.25rem);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 20;
    font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 44ch;
    align-self: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .strip { padding: 4rem 0 5rem; }
    .stat { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
    .stat-num { font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 14vw, 5rem); }
  }

  .about { background: var(--paper); padding: 7rem 0 8rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .about-inner {
    max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 4fr 8fr; gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem); align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1023px) { .about-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; } }
  .about-left { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }
